summary: 'And I hope the sun shines and it's a beautiful day, and something reminds you, you wish you had stayed. You can plan for a...
body: ‘And I hope the sun shines and it’s a beautiful day, and something reminds you, you wish you had stayed. You can plan for a change in weather and time, but I never planned on you changing your mind’. Such a beautiful song. 10 years ago Taylor was alone and heartbroken and now she’s doing better than she ever was and is in the most fulfilling relationship. Nothing makes me happier than @taylorswift being happy
